data.description: New Price! 121st & Sheridan, Bixby North Schools. VA qualifying assumption 2.875% may be available. Single level home, oversized corner lot, $30k in upgrades. Room for a pool. Sophisticated designer features & colors. Home features office w/french doors, 4 bdrm, 3 full bath. Modern floor plan including Mother in Law suite, split bdrm plan & private Primary Suite. Spacious primary bath w/2 vanities & 2 closets (his & hers). Separate Laundry Room w/sink. 3 car garage. Neighborhood amenities include a pool, fitness center, park, walking trails & ponds.
